author: Atomic Shrimp
description:
Very much a sequel. The Purple Jam I made a couple of years ago has all run out, so let's make another batch!  This video goes into a lot of detail about the rationale for some of the methods.

Join the Atomic Shrimp official Discord server for FREE early access to videos! - https://discord.gg/atomicshrimp
Atomic Shrimp subreddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/AtomicShrimp/
